<li> Different top-level installed packages
</li> <li> Test on demand (i.e., on release)
</li></ul> 
<p />
<h3><a name="Long_Term"></a> Long Term </h3> <ul>
<li> Support update/upgrade tests
</li> <li> Support tests involving multiple machines (requires test environment, test categories)
</li> <li> Use osg-test as a post-install step
</li> <li> Better process for turning bug fixes into permanent tests
</li></ul> 
